name: His and hers napkins
description:
100% cotton duck egg napkins with beer mug and cocktail glass designs.
Each pack of napkins has 2 beer mug designs and 2 cocktail glass designs, perfect for a couples' dinnerparty.
Designs are hand-painted onto the napkins, which can be washed at 40 degrees.
Each napkin is 40cm x 40cm
